org.w3.y2001.sw.Europe.skos
Class Binding

java.lang.Object
  org.w3.y2001.sw.Europe.skos.Binding
public class Binding
extends java.lang.Object

A class for a query result binding from an RDF query service. The literalValue, URIvalue and bnodeValue are alternatives.

NOTE: This class is not yet used, it is needed for ServiceBits which is experimental.
